&lt;p&gt;Reports to: CEO &lt;br&gt;Location: Middleburg, VA&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sandboxx is a full life cycle platform serving the military community from the beginning of the military journey through service and beyond. Our work supports service members, their families, and the commands and institutions that surround them. We operate at a national scale, serve millions of users each year, and sit at the intersection of military life, technology, media, and community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our most valuable strategic asset is access to the military community at the moment of accession into service. That access drives early and significant revenue and creates the foundation for the products and services we deliver across every phase of military life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are hiring a Head of Government Relations &amp;amp; Partnerships to lead Sandboxx&#39;s external engagement strategy across government, military, and nonprofit stakeholders. This is both a growth role and a durability role. We need a hunter who can open new doors across the services, the Department of War, and Congress, and an institutional operator who can protect and expand the relationships that already power the business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are hiring a Head of Government Relations &amp;amp; Partnerships to lead Sandboxx&#39;s external engagement strategy across government, military, nonprofit, and community stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting directly to the CEO, you&#39;ll serve as the company&#39;s lead for government relations, public affairs, partnerships with the non-commercial military ecosystem, and external engagement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role sits at the intersection of policy, business development, partnerships, and ecosystem strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll build relationships with congressional offices, Department of War stakeholders, military and veteran service organizations, military family advocacy groups, educational institutions, and nonprofit organizations that share our mission of supporting service members and their families.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Success in this role is measured by outcomes, not activity. We are looking for someone who can translate relationships into partnerships, partnerships into tangible opportunities, and opportunities into measurable impact for the business and the military community we serve.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why We Are Hiring For This Role Now&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sandboxx has grown from a single-product company into a multi-product platform serving the military-connected community across communications, media, readiness, and community engagement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As we continue to scale, we see significant opportunities to deepen our relationships with:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Congressional and government stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Department of War and military commands&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Military family readiness organizations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Veteran service organizations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recruiting and personnel-focused organizations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Military-focused nonprofits and advocacy groups&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Educational institutions serving the military community&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
